Package: TurtleGraphics
Version: 1.0-2
Date: 2014-05-26
Title: Learn computer programming while having a jolly time
Authors@R: c(
    person("Anna", "Cena", role = c("aut")),
    person("Marek", "Gagolewski", role = c("aut")),
    person("Marcin", "Kosinski", role = c("aut")),
